Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
i think this is a good thing. freshman year can be scary, especially if youre going somewhere far away and not knowing anyone. making all freshmen live on campus can help to make friends and make them feel more comfortable. it also can help to show that everyone is equal, and can help build friendships down the road by making shared memories. 